{
  "stem": "13251.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And sometimes it would shake like an earthquake.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Always asked-- always asked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother was the one who used to ask a lot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to always worry more about him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hopefully soon, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, you know, the older we got, and the more we realized what was going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like when-- when the war was over, '45-- how old was I? 12-- right?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were old enough to understand from the information that was coming out with all the-- you know, concentration camps, and all that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we hadn't had any mail since 19-- the last time we got mail was in '43.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was a-- a letter that was late in coming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think it was mailed in '41-- two years later.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have no idea how that letter finally got to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's when we heard that we had another brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From the-- from the Jewish ghetto in Bratislava-- yeah, from Judengasse, it was called.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Judengasse means Jewish street.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's German for-- I don't member the address, but I remember it was-- came from Judengasse, in Bratislava, which is the Jewish ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that's where my-- my parents were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I couldn't read in those days, Czech or-- it was-- probably was in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So one of the older kids kind of read it to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think his name was Alex Singer-- I still remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't remember what that letter said, except that we had another brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the only thing that was significant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And his name was Irwin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was born in '41, I guess.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- that was the last letter we got from my parents, yeah, so-- you know, when the war ended.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
